# Claudefish Texel Tuning Positions
# Format: FEN | result (1.0=white win, 0.0=black win, 0.5=draw)
# These are from well-known games and test suites
# Start with quiet positions (no captures or checks in progress)

# Starting position
rnbqkbnr/pppppppp/8/8/8/8/PPPPPPPP/RNBQKBNR w KQkq - 0 1 | 0.5

